text: Mike Schatz is an American voice actor. He is best known for voicing Emory on the Adult Swim program Aqua Teen Hunger Force and the movie Aqua Teen Hunger Force Colon Film movie for Theaters.Mike Schatz interviewed by Banterist He also voiced Torpedo Vegas on Frisky Dingo and he played a guy in court on an episode of Squidbillies. ==References== Category:Year of birth missing (living people) Category:Living people Category:Aqua Teen Hunger Force Category:American voice actors
